OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cattacking Hanley riot cops
OL,6,FA former police officer is in prison
OL,7,Ffor his role in the Hanley riots.
OL,9,FJames Fernandes could be seen on the
OL,10,Ffront-line during the August 3 unrest.
OL,12,FStoke-on-Trent Crown Court heard how
OL,13,FFernandes tried to bowl over police
OL,14,Fwith heavy-footed kicks while
OL,15,Fencouraging violence in others. At the
OL,16,Fheight of the disorder, he branded the
OL,17,Fresponding officers as "scum".
