OL,6,FBodycam footage played to the court
OL,7,Fshowed Fernandes - who has one
OL,8,Fprevious conviction of assault -
OL,9,Fattacking police.
OL,11,FProsecutor Emma Swindell asserted that
OL,12,F"this was a racially-aggravated
OL,13,Foffence".
OL,15,FShe said: "The defendant played an
OL,16,Factive role on the front-lines,
OL,17,Fencouraging disorder.
