OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cattacking Hanley riot cops
OL,6,FHe was spotted at Upper Hillchurch
OL,7,FStreet shouting "come on" to other
OL,8,Fprotesters while threatening police
OL,9,Fofficers.
OL,11,FHe remarked: 'It's our country', in
OL,12,Fone piece of footage."JAfter reviewing
OL,13,Fthe footage, officers quickly
OL,14,Fidentified Fernandes and arrested him
OL,15,Fon August 22.
OL,17,FWhen quizzed by police, he admitted
OL,18,Fkicking the officers' shields, but
OL,19,Fdenied being threatening or
OL,20,Fencouraging violence. He also denied
OL,21,Fbeing racist.
