OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cattacking Hanley riot cops
OL,6,FFernandes, of Compton Street, Hanley,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to one count of violent
OL,8,Fdisorder - despite previously pleading
OL,9,Fnot guilty.
OL,11,FMartin Bloor, mitigating, said: "It
OL,12,Ftook some time for him to come to
OL,13,Fterms with what he'd done. He shows
OL,14,Fdeep remorse for his actions.
OL,16,F"He was there with a friend, but when
OL,17,Fhe saw there was a protest in the
OL,18,Farea, he decided to attend. He had
OL,19,Fassumed it was a peaceful
OL,20,Fdemonstration. Unfortunately, he chose
OL,21,Fto stay when things became violent.
OL,26,@sD@aOU
