OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cattacking Hanley riot cops
OL,6,F"He had a very difficult start in
OL,7,Flife. His parents did not get on and
OL,8,Fthere was often violence at home. He
OL,9,Fspent some time in the care of his
OL,10,Fgrandparents and some in that of the
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,F"He has always worked hard in full-
OL,14,Ftime employment. He joined the Army,
OL,15,Fbut left due to health issues. He then
OL,16,Fjoined the Royal Gibraltar Police. His
OL,17,Ftime on the force has made him
OL,18,Fespecially regretful of his actions."
