OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after
OL,4,Cattacking Hanley riot cops
OL,6,FThe 30-year-old was handed a 28-month
OL,7,Fprison sentence. He must serve at
OL,8,Fleast 40 per cent before becoming
OL,9,Feligible for release on licence.
OL,11,FJudge Richard McConaghy said: "Police
OL,12,Fwho tried to maintain order as part of
OL,13,Ftheir lawful duty were abused and
OL,14,Fthreatened by people keen to start
OL,15,Fviolence. You were an active
OL,16,Fparticipant in that disorder.
OL,18,F"Throughout the footage, you can be
OL,19,Fheard making comments about 'our
OL,20,Fcountry' and paying tax. At one point,
OL,21,Fyou made a remark about a 'civil war'.
OL,26,@sD@_OU
