OL,6,F"Your motivations and intentions were
OL,7,Fquite clear. At your worst, you were
OL,8,Finvolved in direct action against
OL,9,Fpolice officers.
OL,11,F"As a former police officer, albeit in
OL,12,Fa different jurisdiction, you should
OL,13,Fhave been keenly aware of their
OL,14,Fposition."
